description: This is a market on whether Hikaru Nakamura will get 9 or more points in the preliminaries of the FTX Crypto Cup. The market will resolve to “Yes” if Hikaru Nakamura gets 9 or more points during the preliminaries of the FTX Crypto Cup, and “No” otherwise. If any of Hikaru’s preliminary games are postponed to a day on or before May 31, 2021, they will be considered for market resolution. If any of Hikaru’s preliminary games are postponed to a day after May 31, 2021, or cancelled altogether, they will not be considered for market resolution. In the event of ambiguity in terms of the market outcome, the market will be resolved in good faith at the sole discretion of the Markets Integrity Committee (MIC).
